(en) Party of North Vi 1943. On the left, the church of the parish appears in 1771. On the cape on the right is Ribbinghov’s seal. The main building was built in 1692 by Major General Axel von Schaars. In 1806 a second floor was built.
The photograph is a contact-copied work material that does not make the airline’s finished postcard fair - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFB000537. AB Flygtrafik. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021016419854. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
